{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji28.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给毛宇居的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给毛宇居?的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年5月15日）宇居兄："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"选接数函，极为感谢。乡间情形，尚望随时示知。邹普勋（亨二）如十分困难，病情又重时，如兄手中宽裕时，请酌为接济若千，容后由弟归还。另纸请交邹普勋为祷。即颂健康"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五○、五月十五日[1]毛宇居，毛泽东的堂兄和少年时的私老师。[2]邹普勋，小名亨二，毛泽东少年时的私同学和邻居。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":5,"day":15}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":392,"page_end":392},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}